description:
A powerful clipboard manager that combines your clipboard history, emojis, GIFs, kaomojis, and symbols into a single, searchable interface.

External Services:
• Tenor & Imgur - GIF search and browsing
• Google S2 Favicons - Favicon fallback for URLs
